Dining philosophers
--------------------
The standard problem. Modeled by Radek Pelanek.

Parameters
----------
N=x 	 -- the number of philosophers (default N=4)
LEFT=0/1 -- if there is one left handed philosopher (default LEFT=0)
ROOM=x	 -- solution with limited room, parameter gives the capacity of 
            the room, if x=0 then room is not considered (default ROOM=0)
